DataElement.preferredName: Non-Protocol Therapeutic Procedure Tyrosine Kinase Inhibitor Administered Begin Date
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The start date related to the administration of a non-protocol tyrosine kinase inhibitor therapy, any substance that inhibits tyrosine kinase, an enzyme involved in the transduction and processing of many extracellular and intracellular signals including cell proliferation.
